nodes.text: Uchinao was a small, inhabited planet located in the Five Points system of the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories. Uchinao had a pale, non-water liquid surface with icebergs floating on the surface. The ice was dark and veined with yellow. Massive metal rigs were built on the surface of the bergs. The cities had cramped streets filled with garbage.
Uchinao was shown on the ancient star chart in the Jedi temple located on the moon of Harkrova I.
